will never get the big

00:48:31.700 --> 00:48:33.650
hit that makes you successful.

00:48:33.650 --> 00:48:35.750
But I think over 50% is a
great goal to shoot at.

00:48:35.750 --> 00:48:38.870
But, by the way, that is
an intuitive, visionary

00:48:38.870 --> 00:48:39.590
viewpoint of things.

00:48:39.590 --> 00:48:42.080
