00:48:53.130 --> 00:48:54.820
It was like, come on, guys!

00:48:54.820 --> 00:48:57.490
But I can show you all the
predictions we made back then.

00:48:57.490 --> 00:48:58.230
Dead on.

00:48:58.230 --> 00:48:59.460
100%.

00:48:59.460 --> 00:49:02.350
At least I think so, from
my perspective.

